    header
      h1#header-title
        a(href="/worship_helps/") WorshipHelps
      h2#header-desc A collection of resources and commentary for those who plan and lead weekly Christian worship
    #column-wrapper 
      .column-grid-root
        .column.col-1-of-3
          section.about
            h4.title About
            .container
              p Welcome! This website is intended for thoughtful but harried worship planners. We invite you to explore the resources available here for planning and leading worship.
              p Since this is a collaborative effort, we also invite you to contribute. All are welcome to comment freely; if you are interested in becoming a posting member of this community, please click here.
              p If you don't want to post regularly, but do have a question, or want us the community to address a particular issue, feel free to email.
          section.contributers
            h4.title Contributers
            .container
              .li Tom Trinidad
              .li Thomas Nelson
              .li Taylor Burton-Edwards
              .li Ron Rienstra
              .li Peter Armstrong
              .li Kevin Anderson
              .li Kent Hendricks
